### toRawOccurrenceRecord(node: HyperindexOccurrenceNode): RawOccurrenceRecord

Maps a Hyperindex occurrence node to the RawOccurrenceRecord shape used in:
- src/app/(map-routes)/(main)/_hooks/use-organization-measured-trees.ts (type at line 32)
- src/app/(map-routes)/(main)/_hooks/use-organization-occurrences.ts (type at line 55)
